properties.Name: OrderLine
properties.Description: The components of an Order broken down by Product and Quantity, one per line item.

Columns.Name: OrderId
Columns.Description: The unique number that identifies an Order.

Columns.Name: OrderLineNumber
Columns.Description: The number that identifies the Order Line Item.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: ItemSku
Columns.Description: The Stock Keeping Unit identifier, which is typically used for inventory-related activities.

Columns.Name: Quantity
Columns.Description: The quantity of Product ordered on the order line item.

Columns.Name: ProductListPriceAmount
Columns.Description: The current per unit list price of the Order Line Item products.

Columns.Name: ProductSalesPriceAmount
Columns.Description: The actual per unit selling price of the Order Line Item products.

Columns.Name: ProductAdjustmentAmount
Columns.Description: The per product unit adjustment amount applied to each product unit.

Columns.Name: ProductAdjustmentPercentage
Columns.Description: The per product unit adjustment percentage applied to each product unit.

Columns.Name: TotalOrderLineAdjustmentAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of adjustment for all order line items.

Columns.Name: TotalOrderLineAmount
Columns.Description: The total amount of line item charges related to the quantity of products sold at the actual selling price less rebates and discounts.

Columns.Name: OrderLineNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the Order Line.

Columns.Name: QuantityBooked
Columns.Description: The quantity of Product booked.

Columns.Name: QuantityBilled
Columns.Description: The quantity billed.

Columns.Name: QuantityBacklog
Columns.Description: The quantity on backlog.

Columns.Name: AcceptedQuantity
Columns.Description: The quantity of Order Line Item products accepted.

Columns.Name: QuantityCancelled
Columns.Description: The quantity of Order Line Items cancelled.

Columns.Name: QuantityReturned
Columns.Description: The quantity of Order Line Items returned.

Columns.Name: BookedDate
Columns.Description: The booked date of the Order Line Items.

Columns.Name: BilledDate
Columns.Description: The billed date of the Order Line Items.

Columns.Name: CancelledTimestamp
Columns.Description: The date  and time that Order Line Items were cancelled.

Columns.Name: ReturnedDate
Columns.Description: The date that Order Line Items were returned.

Columns.Name: RequestedDeliveryDate
Columns.Description: The date for delivery of the Order Line Item requested by the Customer/Customer Account.

Columns.Name: CommittedDeliveryDate
Columns.Description: The date committed for delivery of the Order Line Item.

Columns.Name: PlannedPickDate
Columns.Description: The planned inventory pick date for the Order Line Items.

Columns.Name: ActualPickTimestamp
Columns.Description: The actual inventory pick timestamp for the Order Line Items.

Columns.Name: PlannedShipmentDate
Columns.Description: The planned shipment date of the Order Line Items.

Columns.Name: ActualShipmentTimestamp
Columns.Description: The actual shipment timestamp of the Order Line Items.

Columns.Name: PlannedDeliveryDate
Columns.Description: The planned delivery date of the Order Line Items.

Columns.Name: ActualDeliveryTimestamp
Columns.Description: The actual delivery timestamp of the Order Line Items.

Columns.Name: ShipmentConfirmationTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp that the shipment confirmation notice was sent to the Customer/Customer Account.

Columns.Name: DropShipOrderLineItemIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the Order Line Item(s) are to be drop shipped.

Columns.Name: WaybillNumber
Columns.Description: The shipment waybill number.

Columns.Name: TareWeight
Columns.Description: The weight of the line items excluding packaging.

Columns.Name: NetWeight
Columns.Description: The weight of the line items including packaging.

Columns.Name: WeightUomId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Unit Of Measure.

Columns.Name: EarliestDeliveryWindowTimestamp
Columns.Description: The earliest timestamp that the order should be made available for delivery.

Columns.Name: LatestDeliveryWindowTimestamp
Columns.Description: The latest timestamp that the order should be made available for delivery.

Columns.Name: ReturnOrderId
Columns.Description: The unique number that identifies an Order.

Columns.Name: ReturnOrderLineNumber
Columns.Description: The number that identifies the Order Line Item.

Columns.Name: ReturnToStockIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the Line Item(s) were returned to stock.

Columns.Name: ReturnToStoreIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the Line Item(s) were returned to the store from which they were purchased.

Columns.Name: OrderLineTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Order Line Type.

Columns.Name: RejectionReasonId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Rejection Reason.

Columns.Name: WorkOrderId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Work Order.

Columns.Name: TaskId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Task.

Columns.Name: BuyClassId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Buy Class.

Columns.Name: PromotionOfferId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Promotion Offer. The Promotion Offer ID is unique to each account or party that is offered to.
